channel.title: ComplexityRSPS V1.0 ( Pking source, no anti leech. )
channel.description:
[center] [img]http://i.imgur.com/0DH73g2.png[/img] Hello, [B][COLOR="#FF0000"]first off i'm not going to make a huge thread because this source is very basic[/COLOR][/B]. I'm releasing older version of ComplexityRSPS i don't think it's very good but it's good for people whos looking for a pking server.
[B]Credits: Sanity Pim Orel Melody Me Flavorless Fab[/B]
[B]Media:[/B]
[img]https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/64496889/playercount2.png[/img] [youtubeI]http://youtu.be/oCkK40uC8uI[/youtube]
[B]Download Link:[/B] Enoughleeches.
Don't like it, don't use it. also i'm not closing complexity we just have upgraded our source and possibly moving further.
Ps. it's elevation base we cleaned exploits and fixed some packets and a ton of dupes.
[QUOTE=Melody;4070096]Just so people know there is one dupe in this source that I'm aware of, in Walking.java find:
[CODE]if(c.inTrade) { c.getTradeAndDuel().declineTrade(true); } [/CODE]
Replace with:
[CODE]if(c.inTrade) { } [/CODE][/QUOTE]
[U][SIZE=3]No Anti leech.[/SIZE][/U]
[/CENTER]
